  "industry_note": "Aluminum Matrix Composite (MMC) — Al 6061 / 7075 / 2024 + SiC particulate (10-25 vol%). DURALCAN F3S.20S (Al-Si + 20% SiC). σy 380-500 / UTS 450-600 / El 1-5% (brittle increase with SiC) / E 95-120 GPa (Al 의 1.4×). 자동차 brake rotor (Porsche / Audi 일부 모델 — 6061 + 20% SiC, 50% weight reduction vs cast iron), 자전거 frame, F1 piston liner. ⚠ 가공 어려움 — PCD (Diamond) tool 만 가능 (SiC particle → tool wear). 가격 일반 Al 의 5-10×."
